    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't know... it just feels like i'm just idling now. like i'm standing at a terminal waiting for a flight that isn't even on the board anymore. everything i wanted to see, i've seen. the colors of the sunset and all that... it's just light and shadow. it doesn't actually change anything. it just feels like i'm finished with this part of the trip.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
